      <title>挖矿还是建矿场？这是一个问题。</title>
      <link>https://tongxiaofeng.com/posts/2017-11-25-%E6%8C%96%E7%9F%BF%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E5%BB%BA%E7%9F%BF%E5%9C%BA%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link>
